    "long_instructions": "## Brainstorming Initial Ideas Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you come up with early ideas for your product launch.\r\n\r\nFocus on ideas that connect to your assigned role (e.g., name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to brainstorm creative possibilities for your product or campaign.\r\n    - What could this product include or do?\r\n    - What are some possible names, taglines, looks, sounds, or messages?\r\n    - How might this appeal to students to solve a real problem?\r\n2. In your Activity Guide under Stage 2: Brainstorming Initial Ideas, write:\r\n\t- The question or prompt you gave to AI\r\n\t- A summary of what the AI told you\r\n3. Want better results? Try asking AI to give you options in different styles—like playful, futuristic, sleek, or tech-savvy.",
